CustomField.description: ANZARD defines a cleavage embryo as an embryo that is one to four days old, after fertilisation. For embryo recipient cycles, use this data item to record the number of received, vitrified cleavage- stage embryos being warmed in the cycle. If fresh embryos were received, use N_EMBREC_FRESH data item instead.
CustomField.label: ANZARD - Number of vitrified cleavage- s
